Introduction

jojo, also known as JoHa, is a South Korean singer-songwriter and composer under Music Classico and PLANHEAR. She is a part of the duo LEWYN & JoHa.

She made her solo debut on June 1, 2019 with the digital single Eolleli Kkolleli.
